header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-server")
                span 서버
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서버 관리

main(class="servers-page space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="servers-detail-grid", [class.servers-detail-grid-expanded]="terminalExpandedView()")
        aside(*ngIf="!terminalExpandedView() && !isServerDetailScreen()", class="min-w-0 space-y-5")
            section(class="overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", data-testid="servers-node-list")
                div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서버 보드
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서버 목록은 20개 단위로 표시하고 상세는 별도 화면에서 엽니다.
                    div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                        span(class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300") 중심 {{localMasterCount()}}
                        span(class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") 일반 {{workerCount()}}
                        span(class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") {{nodesBoardSummary()}}
                        button(type="button", (click)="openAddServer()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                            span 서버 추가
                div(*ngIf="nodes().length > 0", class="overflow-x-auto")
                    table(class="w-full min-w-[1120px] table-fixed divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            tr
                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 서버
                                th(class="w-64 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Host
                                th(class="w-28 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 서비스
                                th(class="w-32 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 실행 컨테이너
                                th(class="w-32 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 역할
                                th(class="w-44 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 구성
                        tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                            tr(*ngFor="let node of pagedNodes()", role="button", tabindex="0", [attr.aria-label]="'서버 상세로 이동: ' + (node.name || '')", (click)="selectNode(node)", (keydown.enter)="selectNode(node)", (keydown.space)="$event.preventDefault(); selectNode(node)", class="cursor-pointer align-top transition hover:bg-zinc-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-sky-500 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800/60", [ngClass]="isSelected(node) ? 'bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-950/20' : ''")
                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                    div(class="flex min-w-0 items-center gap-2")
                                        span(*ngIf="isNodeCollecting(node)", class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 shrink-0 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-sky-500 shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(14,165,233,0.18)]", title="정보 수집 중")
                                        p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50", [title]="node.name") {{node.name}}
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300")
                                    div(class="flex min-w-0 items-center gap-2")
                                        span(class="truncate", [title]="nodeHostLabel(node)") {{nodeHostLabel(node)}}
                                        i(role="img", class="fa-solid shrink-0 text-sm", [ngClass]="[nodeStatusIcon(node), nodeStatusIconClass(node)]", [title]="nodeStatusTitle(node)", [attr.aria-label]="nodeStatusTitle(node)")
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300")
                                    span(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{nodeServiceCount(node)}}개
                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300")
                                    span(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50", [title]="nodeContainerCountTitle(node)") {{nodeRunningContainerCount(node)}}개
                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="node.is_local_master ? 'border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300'") {{roleLabel(node)}}
                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                    div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5")
                                        span(class="inline-flex shrink-0 rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="swarmBadgeClass(node)") {{deploymentModeText(node)}}
                div(*ngIf="nodes().length === 0", class="space-y-3 px-4 py-8 text-center")
                    p(class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") 등록된 서버가 없습니다.
                    button(type="button", (click)="openAddServer()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                        span 서버 추가
                div(*ngIf="nodesPagination().total > 0", class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                    p(class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 페이지당 20개
                    wiz-portal-season-pagination([current]="nodesPagination().current", [start]="nodesPagination().start", [end]="nodesPagination().end", [maxlength]="10", (pageMove)="moveNodePage($event)")

        section(*ngIf="isServerDetailScreen()", class="min-w-0 space-y-5")
            div(*ngIf="!selected()", class="rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-300 bg-white px-4 py-14 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 서버 보드에서 항목을 선택하세요.

            div(*ngIf="selected()", class="space-y-5", data-testid="servers-detail")
                div(*ngIf="!terminalExpandedView()", class="space-y-5")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                        div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 xl:flex-row xl:items-start xl:justify-between")
                                div(class="min-w-0")
                                    div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                        button(type="button", (click)="closeServerDetail()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left")
                                            span 목록
                                        h2(class="truncate text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{selected()?.name}}
                                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="selected()?.is_local_master ? 'border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300'") {{roleLabel(selected())}}
                                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") IP {{nodeHostLabel(selected())}}
                                        i(role="img", class="fa-solid shrink-0 text-sm", [ngClass]="[nodeStatusIcon(selected()), nodeStatusIconClass(selected())]", [title]="nodeStatusTitle(selected())", [attr.aria-label]="nodeStatusTitle(selected())")
                                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="swarmBadgeClass(selected())") {{deploymentModeText(selected())}}
                                        span(*ngIf="isNodeCollecting(selected())", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300")
                                            span(class="h-2 w-2 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-sky-500")
                                            span 정보 수집 중
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    button(*ngIf="!selected()?.is_local_master", type="button", (click)="openEditServer()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                        span 정보 수정
                                    button(*ngIf="!selected()?.is_local_master", type="button", (click)="openDeleteServer()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                                        span 등록 해제
                                    button(type="button", (click)="checkSelected()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-stethoscope")
                                        span 점검
                                    button(*ngIf="showJoinSwarmButton(selected())", type="button", (click)="joinSelected()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-link")
                                        span Swarm 연결
                        div(class="space-y-3 px-4 py-3")
                            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 xl:flex-row xl:items-center xl:justify-between")
                                p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 화면 값은 선택한 주기로 즉시 확인하고, 장기 자원 기록은 백그라운드에서 10분마다 저장합니다.
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="openResourceChart()", [disabled]="!selected()?.id", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-700 hover:bg-sky-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300 dark:hover:bg-sky-950")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-chart-area")
                                        span 크게 보기
                                    span(*ngIf="detailLoading() || panelRefreshing()", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                                        span {{detailLoading() ? '저장된 상태를 불러오는 중' : '최근 상태를 다시 확인하는 중'}}
                                    span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 자동 갱신
                                    button(*ngFor="let option of refreshOptions", type="button", (click)="setRefreshSeconds(option)", class="inline-flex h-8 min-w-[46px] items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="refreshSeconds() === option ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 bg-white text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'") {{option}}초
                            div(*ngIf="detailError()", class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-amber-700 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-300") {{detailError()}}
                        div(class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-0 divide-x divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0")
                            div(class="p-4", data-testid="servers-cpu")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") CPU
                                p(class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{percent(selected()?.latest_metric?.cpu_percent)}}
                                div(class="mt-3 h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800")
                                    div(class="h-full rounded-full bg-sky-500 transition-all duration-500 ease-out dark:bg-sky-400", [style.width.%]="progressPercent(selected()?.latest_metric?.cpu_percent)")
                            div(class="p-4", data-testid="servers-memory")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Memory
                                p(class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{percent(metricValue('memory.used_percent'))}}
                                div(class="mt-3 h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800")
                                    div(class="h-full rounded-full bg-emerald-500 transition-all duration-500 ease-out dark:bg-emerald-400", [style.width.%]="progressPercent(metricValue('memory.used_percent'))")
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{formatBytes(metricValue('memory.used'))}} / {{formatBytes(metricValue('memory.total'))}}
                            div(class="p-4", data-testid="servers-storage")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Storage
                                p(class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{percent(metricValue('storage.used_percent'))}}
                                div(class="mt-3 h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800")
                                    div(class="h-full rounded-full bg-amber-500 transition-all duration-500 ease-out dark:bg-amber-400", [style.width.%]="progressPercent(metricValue('storage.used_percent'))")
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{formatBytes(metricValue('storage.used'))}} / {{formatBytes(metricValue('storage.total'))}}
                            div(class="p-4")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스
                                p(class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{dockerUnavailable() ? '-' : serviceGroups().length}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{dockerUnavailable() ? 'Docker 사용 불가' : (serviceGroups().length + '개 서비스 관리 중')}}

                section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                            button(type="button", (click)="setDetailTab('overview')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border px-3 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="isDetailTab('overview') ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 bg-white text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-table-columns")
                                span 개요
                            button(type="button", (click)="setDetailTab('files')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border px-3 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="isDetailTab('files') ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 bg-white text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-folder-tree")
                                span 파일
                            button(type="button", (click)="setDetailTab('terminal')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border px-3 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="isDetailTab('terminal') ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 bg-white text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-terminal")
                                span 웹 터미널
                            button(type="button", (click)="setDetailTab('storage')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border px-3 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="isDetailTab('storage') ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 bg-white text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-hard-drive")
                                span 스토리지

                    section(*ngIf="isDetailTab('overview')", class="space-y-4 p-4")
                        section(*ngIf="dockerUnavailable()", class="space-y-4")
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-4 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40")
                                div(class="flex items-start gap-3")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation mt-0.5 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-300")
                                    div
                                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-100") Docker를 사용할 수 없는 서버
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200") {{dockerUnavailableReason()}}
                                        p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300") 이 서버에서는 등록된 서비스 목록을 표시하지 않습니다. Docker 설치 또는 daemon 상태를 먼저 확인해주세요.

                        section(*ngIf="showRuntimePanels()", class="space-y-4", data-testid="servers-containers-table")
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 등록된 서비스
                                    span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{serviceGroups().length}}
                                div(*ngIf="serviceGroups().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 이 서버에서 실행 중인 등록 서비스가 없습니다.
                                div(*ngIf="serviceGroups().length > 0", class="overflow-x-auto")
                                    table(class="min-w-full divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                        thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                            tr
                                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 서비스
                                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 상태
                                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 사용 중인 포트
                                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 일괄 액션
                                                th(class="px-4 py-2 text-right font-semibold") 상세
                                        tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                            tr(*ngFor="let group of serviceGroups()")
                                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                                    p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{serviceDisplayName(group)}}
                                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="serviceRuntimeClass(group)") {{serviceRuntimeLabel(group)}}
                                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                                    div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-1")
                                                        span(*ngFor="let badge of servicePortBadges(group)", class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="servicePortBadgeClass(badge)") {{badge.label}}
                                                    span(*ngIf="servicePortBadges(group).length === 0", class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 연결된 포트 없음
                                                td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                                    div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5")
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="serviceActionTitle(group, 'start')", (click)="runServiceAction(group, 'start')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunServiceAction(group, 'start')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-play")
                                                            span 실행
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="serviceActionTitle(group, 'restart')", (click)="runServiceAction(group, 'restart')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunServiceAction(group, 'restart')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                                                            span 재시작
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="serviceActionTitle(group, 'stop')", (click)="runServiceAction(group, 'stop')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunServiceAction(group, 'stop')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-stop")
                                                            span 중지
                                                td(class="px-4 py-3 text-right")
                                                    a([routerLink]="serviceDetailRoute(group)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square")
                                                        span 서비스 상세

                    section(*ngIf="isDetailTab('files')", class="p-4")
                        wiz-component-file-tree([title]="'서버 파일'", [description]="selected()?.host || ''", [scope]="'node'", [context]="serverFileTreeContext()", [rootLabel]="selected()?.name || 'server'", [allowUpload]="true", [allowMutate]="true", [allowRead]="true")

                    section(*ngIf="isDetailTab('terminal')", class="p-4", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'min-h-[calc(100vh-180px)]' : 'space-y-4'")
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'flex min-h-[calc(100vh-210px)] flex-col' : ''")
                            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="terminalConnected() ? statusClass('ok') : (terminalConnecting() ? statusClass('pending') : statusClass('unknown'))") {{terminalStatus()}}
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    button(type="button", data-testid="servers-terminal-expand-toggle", (click)="toggleTerminalExpanded()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'fa-compress' : 'fa-expand'")
                                        span {{terminalExpandLabel()}}
                                    button(type="button", (click)="disconnectTerminal()", [disabled]="!terminalConnected() && !terminalConnecting()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plug-circle-xmark")
                                        span 연결 종료
                                    button(type="button", (click)="clearTerminal()", [disabled]="!terminalConnected()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-eraser")
                                        span 화면 지우기
                            div(class="p-4", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'flex flex-1 flex-col' : ''")
                                div(class="mb-4 flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                                    div
                                        p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 웹 터미널
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{terminalDescription()}}
                                        p(*ngIf="terminalError()", class="mt-2 text-xs text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-300") {{terminalError()}}
                                    button(type="button", (click)="connectTerminal()", [disabled]="busy() || terminalConnecting()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plug")
                                        span {{terminalConnected() ? '다시 연결' : '터미널 연결'}}
                                div(data-testid="servers-terminal-host", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-800 bg-black", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'min-h-[calc(100vh-340px)] flex-1' : 'min-h-[460px]'")

                    section(*ngIf="isDetailTab('storage')", class="space-y-4 p-4", data-testid="servers-storage-mode")
                        div(*ngIf="!isSwarmConnected(selected())", data-testid="servers-storage-independent-warning", class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-800 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-200")
                            div(class="flex gap-3")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-circle-info mt-0.5 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-300")
                                div
                                    p(class="font-semibold") 아직 Swarm 클러스터로 연결되어 있지 않아 스토리지를 적용할 수 없습니다.
                        ng-container(*ngIf="isSwarmConnected(selected())")
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                div(class="flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 py-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between")
                                    div(class="min-w-0")
                                        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                            p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서버 모드
                                            span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="swarmBadgeClass(selected())") {{deploymentModeText(selected())}}
                                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{serverModeDescription(selected())}}
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{serverModeLimitText(selected())}}
                                        p(*ngIf="selectedSwarmNodeId()", class="mt-3 break-all text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") swarm_node_id: {{selectedSwarmNodeId()}}
                                    div(class="flex shrink-0 flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                        button(*ngIf="showOsdSlotWizardButton(selected())", type="button", (click)="openStorageOsdWizard()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-hard-drive")
                                            span OSD 슬롯 구성 마법사
                            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3")
                                div(*ngFor="let row of storageModeRows(selected())", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{row.label}}
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{row.value}}

div(*ngIf="resourceChartOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/60", (click)="closeResourceChart()")
    section(class="relative flex max-h-[92vh] w-full max-w-6xl flex-col rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
            div
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서버 자원 추이
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{selected()?.name || '-'}} · {{resourceHistorySummaryText()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closeResourceChart()", [disabled]="resourceHistoryBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 overflow-auto px-5 py-4")
            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between")
                div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 시작일
                        input(type="date", [ngModel]="resourceHistoryStartDate()", (ngModelChange)="resourceHistoryStartDate.set($event)", class="h-9 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 종료일
                        input(type="date", [ngModel]="resourceHistoryEndDate()", (ngModelChange)="resourceHistoryEndDate.set($event)", class="h-9 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100")
                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                    button(type="button", (click)="loadResourceHistory()", [disabled]="resourceHistoryBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="resourceHistoryBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-chart-line'")
                        span 조회
                    button(type="button", (click)="deleteResourceHistoryRange()", [disabled]="resourceHistoryBusy() || resourceRows().length === 0", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                        span 기간 삭제
            div(*ngIf="resourceHistoryError()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{resourceHistoryError()}}
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3")
                div(class="rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-3 py-3 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40")
                    p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300") CPU
                    p(class="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{latestResourcePercent('cpu_percent')}}
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{resourceStatSummary('cpu_percent')}}
                div(class="rounded-md border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-3 dark:border-emerald-900/70 dark:bg-emerald-950/40")
                    p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300") Memory
                    p(class="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{latestResourcePercent('memory_used_percent')}}
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{resourceStatSummary('memory_used_percent')}}
                div(class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-3 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40")
                    p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300") Storage
                    p(class="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{latestResourcePercent('storage_used_percent')}}
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{resourceStatSummary('storage_used_percent')}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(*ngIf="resourceHistoryBusy() && resourceRows().length === 0", class="flex h-80 items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                    span 자원 기록을 불러오는 중입니다.
                div(*ngIf="!resourceHistoryBusy() && resourceRows().length === 0", class="flex h-80 items-center justify-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 선택한 기간에 표시할 기록이 없습니다.
                div(*ngIf="resourceRows().length > 0", class="divide-y divide-zinc-200 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                    div(class="pb-5")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                            p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") CPU
                            p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 평균 + min/max 범위
                        div(data-resource-chart="cpu", class="mt-2 h-72")
                    div(class="py-5")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                            p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Memory
                            p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 평균 + min/max 범위
                        div(data-resource-chart="memory", class="mt-2 h-72")
                    div(class="pt-5")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                            p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Storage
                            p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 사용률
                        div(data-resource-chart="storage", class="mt-2 h-72")

div(*ngIf="serverModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeServerModal()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-lg rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{serverModalTitle()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closeServerModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 px-5 py-4")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서버 IP 또는 host
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.host", placeholder="192.168.0.15", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-[1fr_120px]")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SSH 계정
                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.username", placeholder="root", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SSH 포트
                    input(type="number", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.ssh_port", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SSH 비밀번호 {{isEditing() ? '(선택)' : ''}}
                input(type="password", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.password", autocomplete="new-password", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(*ngIf="isEditing()", class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 비워두면 저장된 SSH key로 다시 연결 확인한 뒤 저장합니다.
                p(*ngIf="!isEditing()", class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록 중 관리용 SSH key를 저장하고 `snap install oras --classic`으로 ORAS를 설치합니다.
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시 이름
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.name", placeholder="비워두면 host를 사용합니다", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeServerModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveServer()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-key")
                span {{serverSubmitLabel()}}

div(*ngIf="deleteModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/60", (click)="closeDeleteModal()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-lg rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-rose-100 px-5 py-4 dark:border-rose-900/50")
            div
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-rose-700 dark:text-rose-300") 서버 등록 해제
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{deletingNode()?.host || '-'}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closeDeleteModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 px-5 py-4")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-3 py-3 text-sm text-rose-800 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-200")
                p(class="font-semibold") {{deleteConfirmName()}} 서버의 등록 정보를 삭제합니다.
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs") 대상 서버의 자원 수집 agent, 선택적 Swarm 연결, 관리용 SSH 공개키를 제거한 뒤 마스터의 등록 정보와 known_hosts를 정리합니다.
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 확인용 서버 이름
                input(type="text", [ngModel]="deleteConfirmInput()", (ngModelChange)="deleteConfirmInput.set($event)", [placeholder]="deleteConfirmName()", autocomplete="off", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 위 서버 이름과 완전히 같아야 등록 해제가 가능합니다.
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeDeleteModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="unregisterSelectedServer()", [disabled]="busy() || !deleteConfirmMatches()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-rose-600 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-rose-700 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-rose-500 dark:hover:bg-rose-400")
                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="busy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-trash'")
                span {{deleteSubmitLabel()}}

div(*ngIf="fileBrowserOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeFileBrowser()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-3xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", data-testid="servers-compose-browser")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Compose 파일 선택
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{importCandidate()?.name || importCandidate()?.id || '선택한 서버'}}의 docker-compose.yaml 또는 docker-compose.yml 파일을 서비스 생성 화면으로 가져옵니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeFileBrowser()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 px-5 py-4")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 이름
                input(data-testid="servers-compose-service-name", type="text", [ngModel]="composeImportName()", (ngModelChange)="composeImportName.set($event)", placeholder="예: 사내 게시판", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 생성 화면에서 이름, 도메인, 배포 전 점검을 이어서 확인합니다.
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto_auto]")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 경로
                    input(data-testid="servers-compose-path", type="text", [ngModel]="fileBrowserInput()", (ngModelChange)="fileBrowserInput.set($event)", (keydown.enter)="jumpToBrowsePath()", placeholder="예: /home/admin 또는 ~/stack", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                button(type="button", (click)="jumpToBrowsePath()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right")
                    span 이동
                button(type="button", (click)="browseFiles('')", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-house")
                    span 홈
                button(type="button", (click)="toggleHiddenFiles()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="fileBrowserShowHidden() ? 'fa-eye-slash' : 'fa-eye'")
                    span {{fileBrowserShowHidden() ? '숨김 감추기' : '숨김 보기'}}
            div(*ngIf="!fileBrowserPath() && fileBrowserBusy()", class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                span 등록된 사용자 홈 디렉토리를 확인하는 중입니다.
            div(*ngIf="fileBrowserPath()", class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                button(*ngFor="let crumb of fileBrowserCrumbs()", type="button", (click)="browseFiles(crumb.path)", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") {{crumb.label}}
                button(*ngIf="fileBrowserPath() !== '/'", type="button", (click)="browseParent()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up")
                    span 상위 폴더
            div(class="max-h-[420px] overflow-auto rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                div(*ngIf="fileBrowserBusy() && fileBrowserItems().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 파일 목록을 불러오는 중입니다.
                div(*ngIf="!fileBrowserBusy() && fileBrowserItems().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 파일이 없습니다.
                div(*ngFor="let item of fileBrowserItems()", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-100 px-4 py-3 last:border-b-0 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div(class="min-w-0")
                        button(*ngIf="item.type === 'folder'", type="button", (click)="browseFiles(item.path)", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 hover:text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-50 dark:hover:text-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-folder text-amber-500")
                            span(class="truncate") {{item.name}}
                        div(*ngIf="item.type !== 'folder'", class="flex items-center gap-2")
                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="canImportFile(item) ? 'fa-file-code text-sky-500' : 'fa-file text-zinc-400'")
                            p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{item.name}}
                        p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.path}}
                    div(class="flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2")
                        span(*ngIf="item.type === 'folder'", class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 폴더
                        span(*ngIf="item.type === 'file' && !canImportFile(item)", class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록 불가
                        button(*ngIf="canImportFile(item)", type="button", (click)="importComposeFile(item)", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy() || !composeImportNameValue()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                            span 생성 화면으로 이동

div(*ngIf="actionModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeActionModal()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{actionTitle()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closeActionModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-3 px-5 py-4")
            div(*ngFor="let row of actionRows()", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800")
                div(class="min-w-0")
                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{row.name}}
                    p(*ngIf="row.value", class="mt-0.5 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{row.value}}
                span(class="inline-flex shrink-0 rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(row.status)") {{statusLabel(row.status)}}
            div(*ngIf="actionResult()?.service", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 text-sm dark:border-zinc-800")
                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{actionResult()?.service?.name || actionResult()?.service?.namespace}}
                p(class="mt-1 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{actionResult()?.compose_path || '-'}}
            div(*ngIf="actionResult()?.operation", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 text-sm dark:border-zinc-800")
                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 작업 {{actionResult()?.operation?.status || '-'}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{actionResult()?.operation?.type || 'operation'}} · {{actionResult()?.macro?.name || '-'}}
                pre(*ngIf="actionOperationLogText()", class="mt-3 max-h-72 overflow-auto rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-100") {{actionOperationLogText()}}
            div(*ngIf="actionRows().length === 0 && !actionResult()?.service", class="py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 결과가 없습니다.
        div(class="flex justify-end border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeActionModal()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200") 확인
